ANTsRCore 0.6.3.2
  • Reference

Extract or Replace Parts of antsImage Object

brackets.Rd

Operators acting on antsImage objects to extract or replace parts.

# S4 method for antsImage,`NULL`,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,logical,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,array,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,matrix,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,list,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,antsImage,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,`NULL`,antsRegion,ANY
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,logical,antsRegion,ANY
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,array,antsRegion,ANY
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,matrix,antsRegion,ANY
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,`NULL`,`NULL`,numeric
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,numeric,numeric,numeric
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,numeric,`NULL`,numeric
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,`NULL`,numeric,numeric
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,numeric,missing,array
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,missing,numeric,array
[(x, i, j, ...) <- value

# S4 method for antsImage,`NULL`,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ..., drop = TRUE)

# S4 method for antsImage,antsImage,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ..., drop = TRUE)

# S4 method for ANY,antsImage,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ..., drop = TRUE)

# S4 method for antsImage,logical,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ..., drop = TRUE)

# S4 method for antsImage,logical,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ..., drop = TRUE)

# S4 method for antsImage,ANY,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ..., drop = TRUE)

# S4 method for antsImage,ANY,ANY,ANY
[(x, i, j, ..., drop = TRUE)

# S4 method for antsImage,`NULL`,`NULL`,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA, ...,
  drop)

# S4 method for antsImage,`NULL`,`NULL`,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA, ...,
  drop)

# S4 method for antsImage,numeric,numeric,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA,
  ..., drop)

# S4 method for antsImage,numeric,numeric,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA,
  ..., drop)

# S4 method for antsImage,numeric,`NULL`,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA,
  ..., drop)

# S4 method for antsImage,numeric,`NULL`,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA,
  ..., drop)

# S4 method for antsImage,`NULL`,numeric,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA,
  ..., drop)

# S4 method for antsImage,`NULL`,numeric,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA,
  ..., drop)

# S4 method for antsImage,missing,numeric,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA,
  ..., drop)

# S4 method for antsImage,numeric,missing,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA,
  ..., drop)

# S4 method for antsImage,missing,missing,ANY
[(x, i, j, k = NA, l = NA,
  ..., drop)

Arguments

x

antsImage
i

logical or i-th dimension
j

not used or j-th dimension
...

not used
value

value to assign to the subset in assignment operator
drop

method for missing data
k

not used or k-th dimension
l

not used or l-th dimension

Examples

fi <- antsImageRead(getANTsRData( "r16" ))
l = prod(dim(fi))
sub = sample(c(TRUE, FALSE), size = l, replace = TRUE)
fi[sub] = rnorm(sum(sub))
fi[,1] = array(10, dim = dim(fi[, 1]))

fi <- antsImageRead(getANTsRData( "ch2" ))
